  "body": "Reference: https://blog.ethereum.org/2016/11/18/hard-fork-no-4-spurious-dragon/\r\n\r\n### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nThe spurious dragon hard fork contains the following rule changes:\r\n\r\n* [EIP155](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/155): Transaction replay protection\r\n* [EIP160](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/160): EXP cost increase\r\n* [EIP161](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/161): State trie clearing\r\n* [EIP170](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/issues/170): Contract code-size limit\r\n\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\n* EIP155 implementation: https://gist.github.com/pipermerriam/38602f2ea4b2ebd762410f0afaa599d1\r\n* EIP160: Subclass the opcode and increase the gas price.\r\n* EIP161: TODO\r\n* EIP170: TODO\r\n",
